	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Maxime volui, sed non potui verbosissimas ad te scribere literas, ornatissime Bullingere.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iesuitę iam concedunt <placeName type="auto_name">Monachium</placeName>, occupant alioqui splendidum nidum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l231" cert="high">Ingolstadii</placeName>; eorum munus est administrare ludum literarium non tantum Monachii, verum etiam per totam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l619" cert="high">Bavariam</placeName> presidente <persName type="auto_name">Staphylo</persName>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Video, nisi potenti manu adsit dominus, errores papisticos incrudescere et indies magis ingravescere.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magna culpę pars in mutos, elingues et ociosos canes, qui propter ingluviem in rebus publicis maximis consulunt ventri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Canisius</persName> hic in cathedrali ecclesia concionatur; procul dubio aliquid parturit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ago gracias immortales pro <persName type="auto_name">Hieremia</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsit ad me quidam, ut hac monstrat tabula; si poteris iuvare, rogo, facis.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Neogeorgus</placeName> dicitur carmen egregium scripsisse contra Catalogum hereticorum per pontificem damnatorum.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tabellario nihil eroges.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ocyssime.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">22. septembris anno 1559.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2856" cert="high">G[ereon] S[ailerus</persName>] t[uus].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heinricho Bullingero, theologo et amico summa reverentia colendo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
